Augmented Reality on a 4K - four-meter screen!	
We have a camera, a printed marker called a Fiducial, some simple computer vision tracking the marker, and 3D graphics registered on it so that the physical sheet of paper is augmented with the 3D graphics and we are projecting this on the studio wall of 10-square meters and 10 million pixels.
